{
  "stem": "4695.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK, he tell me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can have bread, everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And matter of fact, you will meet people now from Poland is living in this city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a lot Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It is not 1937.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It is now 1940, and we go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Krasnodar.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I come there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I start working it's like only from autos, painting autos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I put my wife in the hospital, and my son was born there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My son's name is Anatol.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was born the 19th of August, 1940.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the life was-- was good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know what has happened to my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know nobody will survive, even--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I know what the Germans will do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know even before the-- I don't know it was going to be gas-- gas chambers, how they will do or just how-- I know they will liquidate the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know the German propaganda, and I know how sure there was with them 1939, how sure what they will do everything, you see?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the [GERMAN], the [GERMAN]--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Superman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The would do-- other nations had not-- not law, anything, only according I see they will leave the Slavic nation so much how much need the German economy.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They will control even the population, how many they need.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it-- it-- it will be no life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I know my family, nobody will-- will survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the Germans attacked Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They went, I think, June. the-- the 21st of June or 22.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The 22nd of June, they attack Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1941.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then they come, like I was telling to my wife, the Russians will not keep the front.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In two months, they come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every day, every day, the Russians retreat, retreat.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
